  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators hypothesize that pregnant women with gestational diabetes will have a high
      incidence of sleep apnea, and that the treatment of sleep apnea will lead to improved glucose
      control in these women.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
